==English==

===Etymology===
Named after Jean-Charles de Borda who devised the system in 1781, although it is claimed he was proceeded by Nicholas of Cusa.

===Noun===
# A [[voting system]] in which [[voter]]s rank [[candidate]]s in order of [[preference]] and points are awarded to candidates based these rankings.  The winning candidate is one with the most points.

